playstore_details.title: Prizm wallet, p2p cryptocurrency exchange
playstore_details.description:
Prizmbit is Wallet with paramining up to 11% / month (PoS coins staking) with peer to peer cryptocurrency exchange. Recharge crypto, replenish fait currencies instantly.

There’s a full pack of finance tools in your pocket!
In addition, get up to 11% passive income per month with Prizm Paramining just for keeping PZM in your wallet.

Let's talk about functionality:

Wallets.

Instantly make transactions with cryptocurrencies Prizm PZM, Bitcoin BTC, Ethereum ETH and Tether USD, and keep your funds in stable fiat currencies Russian Rubles RUB, Euro EUR, U.S. Dollar USD, which can be a deposit and withdrawal from your wallet conveniently via popular payment systems (Visa, MasterCard, SEPA, SWIFT, Qiwi, AdvCash, Alfa bank, Tinkoff, Sberbank and other). View your total account balance in different currencies. Send currency to users with zero fees by using "PrizmBit codes".


P2P exchange.

Buy and sell cryptocurrency directly, without intermediaries. Our service will provide a guarantee of receipt of funds with no fee (0%).

Cryptocurrency Exchange.

Use a wide range of exchange tools inside your application: view charts, rates history, statistics. Top-up, place orders, trade and increase balance of your wallets. Spend more.




Paramining.

There are 3 factors that influence your yield:

1. The number of coins in your personal Prizm wallet
2. The number of coins in followers’ structure
3. Mining difficulty - PARATAX

A three-factor source of increasing the number of coins in your wallet.

The network operates by PoS (proof of stake) algorithm. New coins mining called Paramining. Each purchased PRIZM coin in your wallet instantly leads to beginning generation of new coins.

The speed of mining new coins depends on the number of coins in the wallet - the more coins you have, the higher the rate of paramining, the higher your profitability. Paratax is a linear increase in the difficulty of creating coins, expressed as a percentage of the number of coins already mined by all users.

The maximum limit of PARATAX will be 99% at the time of mining 3 billion PZM.
The higher the percentage of Paratax, the more difficult it is to get new coins.
 Referral system

Using the affiliate program, you can earn together with us, starting to receive rewards in the form of part or full profits from the exchange trading commission of your invited users.


Security.

-The application is always protected by a pin code. For convenience, you can add fingerprint or “Face Unlock”
- Each transaction is protected by a one time password (OTP) that is sent to Your email address.
- You can add more security by turning on 2-factor authentication via Telegram bot (OTP) or authenticator app, like Google (TOTP)
- You can add trusted IP addresses, and have access to the account only using that addresses.
- Notifications about all key actions in the account on e-mail or another way You choose.

We have worked a lot to give You the most convenient, understandable and secure way to experience the world of cryptocurrencies. But we are not going to stop and will continue developing and making great products. Please, share your comments and opinions on our product via prizmbit@gmail.com
